==Swedish==
===Etymology===
From Swedish [[klippa]] for "rock" and German [[dachs]] for "badger"

===Noun===
'''klippdass''' (plural: '''[[klippdassar]]''')

* {{cattag|archaic}} [[Hyrax]] or specifically [[Rock Hyrax]].

====Dictionary notes====
